result.text:
People are quick to say “Manchester City and Chelsea haven’t been punished yet”, whilst you are correct, you fail to realise one thing.

What they have done is significantly, significantly worse than Everton. They can also afford significantly better legal teams to deal with such.

Everton cannot. They are an easier target, which is the sad truth.

The Premier League need to be able to prove what Chelsea and Manchester City have done. If they do, the repercussions will be much,
much worse.

Remember, a large reason FFP was popularised to stop clubs such as Manchester City and Chelsea in the first place.
